com.wookler.zconfig.common.model.nodes

Class ConfigResourceNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wookler.zconfig.common.model.nodes.AbstractConfigNode
      • com.wookler.zconfig.common.model.nodes.ConfigElementNode
        • com.wookler.zconfig.common.model.nodes.ConfigResourceNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConfigResourceFile

    public abstract class ConfigResourceNode
extends ConfigElementNode
    Node denotes a resource URI. Resources specified will be downloaded (if required) and made accessible via the configuration handle.

    XML:

    JSON: resource : { name : "name", URI : "uri", type : "type", ... }
